      <mj-column vertical-align="middle">
        <mj-spacer height="50px"></mj-spacer>
        <mj-text font-size="18px" align="left" color="#ffffff" font-weight="100" font-style="italic" letter-spacing="1px" padding-bottom="2px" font-family="Arial" line-height="1px"><b>Nome do animal 1</b></mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="5px"></mj-spacer>
        <mj-text font-size="14px" align="left" color="#ffffff" font-weight="100" padding-bottom="0px" font-family="Arial" line-height="20px">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent in diam tellus. Donec euismod est quis enim dictum dictum. Phasellus ultrices pellentesque dolor sit amet lobortis. Maecenas viverra, magna eu tincidunt blandit, nisl nulla tempus quam, fermentum lacinia felis velit eget metus. Phasellus auctor dapibus fringilla. Duis rutrum urna orci, eget ultricies nisl commodo mollis. Nulla blandit tincidunt m </mj-text>
